<i>♪ I wish I was there ♪</i>

1169
00:48:18,708 --> 00:48:20,708
<i>♪ Oh please don't let me die ♪</i>

1170
00:48:20,791 --> 00:48:22,875
<i>♪ Waiting for your touch ♪</i>

1171
