<i>[singing in Japanese]</i>

1176
00:48:41,708 --> 00:48:48,666
<i>♪ ♪</i>

1177
00:48:48,750 --> 00:48:52,208
<i>♪ For now I'll see you off ♪</i>

1178
00:48:52,291 --> 00:48:53,958
<i>♪ ♪</i>

1179
00:48:54,041 --> 00:48:57,541
<i>♪ And we'll die</i>
<i>Waiting for a new day ♪</i>

1180
